name: The Rise of Purgatory (Generative Trippy Crystal)
description:
Look into the future through the generative trippy crystals.
"The Rise of Purgatory" from The "Generative Trippy Crystal" Collection by Hhvmid.

12 fps
Loop Video 
1080*1080 

"The Rise of Purgatory" is a video loop made with architectural landscapes and exaggerated color palettes mixed with mathematical algorithm scripts and a Pseudo random number generator (PRNG) to replicate a divination crystal ball.
